(7040, 252, 'rows_0_col3_a', '<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-128 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/maximum-exposure.jpg\" alt=\"maximum-exposure\" width=\"750\" height=\"492\" />\r\n<h3>Maximum Exposure</h3>\r\nWe are a UK sales agency who work with innovative food and drink entrepreneurs and manufacturers to empower success.\r\n\r\nTogether we will define the best solutions for your brand to gain maximum FMCG sales exposure. We do this in a profitable and ethical way, ensuring brand longevity and integrity.'),
(7041, 252, '_rows_0_col3_a', 'field_5afc1e1c22e5e'),
(7042, 252, 'rows_0_col3_b', '<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-127 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/long-term-partnerships.jpg\" alt=\"long-term-partnerships\" width=\"750\" height=\"492\" />\r\n<h3 class=\"p1\">Long term partnerships</h3>\r\nWe’re never in it for the short term. Our goal is to plan and execute a sales strategy that will lead to long term, sustainable and profitable growth.\r\n\r\nWe work with our clients to constantly review, evaluate and build on successes so you can continue to innovate, launch new products and conquer new markets.'),
(7043, 252, '_rows_0_col3_b', 'field_5afc1e3622e5f'),
(7044, 252, 'rows_0_col3_c', '<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-126 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/forward-thinking-01.jpg\" alt=\"forward-thinking\" width=\"749\" height=\"492\" />\r\n<h3>Forward thinking</h3>\r\nIn a world where retail is constantly evolving, we keep abreast of changes and adjust our strategies and category management accordingly.\r\n\r\nWe are continuously in touch with influential movers and shakers within the industry to ensure we can overcome the challenges that brands face in both the bricks and clicks environment.'),
