(12807, 339, '_cs_rows_0_colour', 'field_5b4f3a7cdbc2a'),
(12808, 339, 'cs_rows_1_column_a', '<h2>Launch</h2>\r\nThere have been many challenges along the way including production and supply chain issues especially as the production line is a world first. Through working together closely we have overcome these hurdles and maintained a good supplier relationship with our retail customers.'),
(12809, 339, '_cs_rows_1_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
(12810, 339, 'cs_rows_1_columns_b', '<div class=\"quote\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"xl\">Nº1</span> Low calorie, low carb rice alternative in the UK <span class=\"name\">Kantar Worldpanel</span>\r\n\r\n</div>'),
(12811, 339, '_cs_rows_1_columns_b', 'field_5b4f3a4ddbc29'),
(12812, 339, 'cs_rows_1_colour', '#00bfb2'),
(12813, 339, '_cs_rows_1_colour', 'field_5b4f3a7cdbc2a'),
(12814, 339, 'cs_rows_2_column_a', '<h2>Results</h2>\r\nCauli Rice has recently launched in both the US and Australia. While Gem focuses on this exciting overseas expansion we continue to mange the sales chain in the UK.\r\n\r\nWe continue to work together to drive this outstanding growth further, launching new products and attracting more and more customers.'),
(12815, 339, '_cs_rows_2_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
(12816, 339, 'cs_rows_2_columns_b', '<div class=\"quote quote2\">\r\n\r\n‘Product Chain’s dedicated sales team have invaluable experience dealing with UK Grocery multiples which has saved us time and anguish along the way. Their intelligent analysis and use of the data has enabled us to work together to formulate the overall strategy for our brand. In addition, the Product Chain Client Service team have been a huge help – I did not realise how much heavy administration is required for dealing with supermarkets! They have freed up my time to concentrate on other essential areas of the business’ <span class=\"name\">Gem Misa, Co-founder</span>\r\n\r\n</div>'),
