(12878, 345, 'cs_rows_1_column_a', '<h2>Launch</h2>\r\nThere have been many challenges along the way including production and supply chain issues especially as the production line is a world first. Through working together closely we have overcome these hurdles and maintained a good supplier relationship with our retail customers.'),
