(12884, 345, 'cs_rows_2_column_a', '<h2>Results</h2>\r\nCauli Rice has recently launched in both the US and Australia. While Gem focuses on this exciting overseas expansion we continue to mange the sales chain in the UK.\r\n\r\nWe continue to work together to drive this outstanding growth further, launching new products and attracting more and more customers.'),
