(19, 1, '2018-06-28 11:45:00', '2018-06-28 10:45:00', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Consultancy</h1>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">Knowledge is Power. We advise clients on the viability of their products and will always suggest ways to improve the chance of take-up by both retailers and consumers alike.</span></h4>\r\nIf there is doubt regarding the viability of a proposition within the UK marketplace, we can conduct bespoke consultancy projects to help inform the final decision. Conducting a thorough market analysis upfront allows all parties to make a more informed choice before embarking on a potentially costly launch programme.', 'Consultancy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'consultancy', '', '', '2018-07-24 14:49:38', '2018-07-24 13:49:38', '', 265, 'http://localhost/product-chain/?page_id=19', 0, 'page', '', 0),
