(21, 1, '2018-06-28 11:45:13', '2018-06-28 10:45:13', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">New Product Launches</h1>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">Passionate About Delivering New Food &amp; Drink Innovation. You’ve developed a fantastic product that looks and tastes great, but how do you get it on retailer shelves?</span></h4>\r\nThere are many hurdles to overcome in the process. A well thought out strategy from the start will help you clear those hurdles as painlessly as possible. This is a process we are very familiar with. We’ve learnt many lessons along the way and apply our learnings to ensure your journey will be as smooth as possible. We’ll help guide you every step of the way and offer practical advice.', 'New Product Launches', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'new-product-launches', '', '', '2018-07-24 17:03:21', '2018-07-24 16:03:21', '', 265, 'http://localhost/product-chain/?page_id=21', 0, 'page', '', 0),
